Announces hunter pounces to the entire server

-command-
"pounceannounce_minimum","0","The minimum amount of damage required to announce the pounce"
"pounceannounce_centerchat","1","Announces the pounce to center chat. Use 0 for regular player chat."
"pounceannounce_showdistance","0","Show the distance the hunter traveled for the pounce."
"pounceannounce_capdamage","0","Caps the displayed pounce damage to the maximum able to be dealt."
